{"tid":2122490,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"醫療輔助隊員染疫 揭訓練日20人慶生","createTime":"2020-07-24T04:33:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-24T09:10:05.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"02cd600cf6aa55005ee81c59c687e1359c23735d","tid":2122490,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T04:33:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200724/TPCZHOBT5RF4J2NSUTFEY6TPFQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200724%2FTPCZHOBT5RF4J2NSUTFEY6TPFQ%2F&d=7JJHJI7m8dwGfBTVwC1i6DizWcNDgH0nsvPDQhA%2BiAk%3D&h=6229fd5d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200724%2FTPCZHOBT5RF4J2NSUTFEY6TPFQ%2F&h=f6b1f4c2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200724/TPCZHOBT5RF4J2NSUTFEY6TPFQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n醫療輔助隊員染疫 揭訓練日20人慶生<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】昨日有多名公務員確診，包括一名43歲在灣仔警察總部毒品調查科工作的女警長、灣仔入境處總部一名職員，以及醫療輔助隊一名駐守行動翼離島區的35歲男志願隊員。據悉該名染疫醫療輔助隊員在確診前曾受訓，當日有20多名隊員違規切蛋糕慶祝某隊員生日，醫療輔助隊表示如有人違規，會按既定程序處理。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：觀塘帝盛變隔離中心 住客急退房<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/ONPp74U3KT-iS_GdtA5cgKY9hB8=/960x960/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/D2KTKVLV4IILBRBIPRKWXREWM4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FONPp74U3KT-iS_GdtA5cgKY9hB8%3D%2F960x960%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FD2KTKVLV4IILBRBIPRKWXREWM4.jpg&h=fb43d4ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n染疫醫療輔助隊員本月12日曾參與訓練，同日有逾20名隊員違規聚餐慶祝生日。讀者提供圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n長洲消防員初步確診<br />\n<br />\n衞生防護中心傳染病處主任張竹君昨表示，。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n張竹君稱，入境處再有一名職員確診，。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n醫療輔助隊證實一名35歲駐守行動翼離島區的男志願隊員確診，。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n長洲消防局昨晚傳出有消防員初步確診。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n機電工程署證實，長沙灣政府合署有兩名冷氣維修承辦商員工染疫，。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n東華三院馮黃鳳亭中學一名34歲男教師（第2178號）確診，。。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"17e3057b7d653d0f3031ee8b461eb682b4de00c7","tid":2122490,"uid":200070,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T04:39:39.000Z","msg":"不嬲成班師奶阿叔係度hea<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n醫療隊大把正職係公墓員廢老<br />\n樓上係廢老邨 門口又大排檔 <br />\n成個訓練中心得廁所有窗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成班人唔通齋切蛋糕唔食咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n買定花生等睇好戲都啱"},{"pid":"1d1b2f9c3132dc7f711ea7edd6f18c4c3477f68b","tid":2122490,"uid":36820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"17e3057b7d653d0f3031ee8b461eb682b4de00c7","tid":2122490,"uid":200070,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T04:39:39.000Z","msg":"不嬲成班師奶阿叔係度hea<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n醫療隊大把正職係公墓員廢老<br />\n樓上係廢老邨 門口又大排檔 <br />\n成個訓練中心得廁所有窗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成班人唔通齋切蛋糕唔食咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n買定花生等睇好戲都啱"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T04:44:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"128a704f2afa035aed0a7d7af92fa372b6d6d7b5","tid":2122490,"uid":170044,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T04:52:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cd1ded1c86575d631116142be5f3c90340f18d47","tid":2122490,"uid":236891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T08:50:18.000Z","msg":"呢啲非常時期重要咁多人眾埋一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />冇資格叫自己做紀律部隊"},{"pid":"bfe9d3bb9c7af51cb5ebc62e13a13bfea08c2e1d","tid":2122490,"uid":268754,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"17e3057b7d653d0f3031ee8b461eb682b4de00c7","tid":2122490,"uid":200070,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T04:39:39.000Z","msg":"不嬲成班師奶阿叔係度hea<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"